das-backup-manager (0.7.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Full management GUI with D-Bus privilege escalation
  * D-Bus helper daemon (btrdasd-helper) with polkit authorization
  * FFI shared library for GUI access to Rust library
  * Sidebar navigation, backup operations panel, health dashboard
  * Dolphin-style file browser, first-run wizard, desktop notifications
  * Shell completions for bash, zsh, fish, elvish, PowerShell
  * Man page (btrdasd.1)

