das-backup-manager (0.5.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaged release
  * Rust indexer with SQLite FTS5 content indexing
  * KDE Plasma 6 GUI for browsing/restoring backup snapshots
  * 5 zsh orchestration scripts for btrbk-based backups
  * systemd service and timer units

